{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Slime Nomi is a pixelated platformer. Help Nomi collect potion ingredients with the help of unique mechanics in various hand-crafted levels. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unique mechanics: Demo contains 2 chapters with 4 original mechanics: teleport potions, shields, breakable boxes and pufferfish.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Varied level design: 60 well-designed levels blending different mechanics. Each level has a different route and experience. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Cute pixel art: Smooth pixel art animations and 2 different scenes. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Moderate difficulty: Difficulty increases gradually.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Map and collectible marks: Level map can be unlocked after beating the demo. The map has marks of savepoints and collectibles, making it easier to explore and collect things. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Custom option: Provide help to beat challenging levels. </p></li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3489750/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1738666278","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3489750/page.bg.jpg?t=1738666278","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3489750/ae45e72c53d7034fff51df07646b49da82f82632/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1738666278","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3489750/ae45e72c53d7034fff51df07646b49da82f82632/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1738666278","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Game demo","id":10},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description"